WEBVTT

00:14:28.518 --> 00:14:30.115
If you can invest more seriously

00:14:30.139 --> 00:14:32.653
and help us over that critical
million-dollar hurdle,

00:14:32.677 --> 00:14:33.844
do that.

00:14:33.868 --> 00:14:36.607
But invest in seeing
the other half of the story.

00:14:38.575 --> 00:14:40.682
Four: disrupt through business.

00:14:41.352 --> 00:14:43.793
So now I'm talking
to all of the businesspeople

00:14:43.817 --> 00:14:45.125
and entrepreneurs.

00:14:45.149 --> 00:14:47.563
This does not happen
very often in the world,

00:14:47.587 --> 00:14:50.183
but right here we have a golden situation

00:14:50.207 --> 00:14:53.028
in which you can enact
significant social change

00:14:53.052 --> 00:14:55.052
while also making money.

00:14:56.274 --> 00:14:59.194
Hollywood is a system ripe for disruption.

00:14:59.218 --> 00:15:02.192
The old models of financing
and distribution are crumbling --